    <description>Closed Loop Stimulation (CLS) is a unique concept in rate-adaptive pacing that uses the natural cardiovascular control loop to determine the appropriate pacing rate. Closed Loop Stimulation is the only rate-adaptive system responding to mental stress and thereby assuring optimal cerebral perfusion in everyday activity.</description>
